column1: Weighted MRI visualization size (256, 128, 1) in T2 of the skull of a man of 37 years old, with axial section n°172 starting at the base of the skull. The following elements are present : the white matter of left cerebral hemisphere of volume 1861.5234 mm³, the cortex of left cerebral hemisphere of volume 3889.1602 mm³, the white matter of right cerebral hemisphere of volume 1905.0293 mm³ and the cortex of right cerebral hemisphere of volume 3986.7188 mm³.
